trans-unit.source: Represents a <see cref="T:System.Type" /> property (and its value) of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: 表示列印系統硬體或軟體元件的 <see cref="T:System.Type" /> 屬性 (及其值)。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The name of the property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty" /> represents.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty" /> class that has the specified property name.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty" /> 類別的新執行個體，此類別有指定的屬性名稱。

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Type> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: `attributeName`拼字應該做為某些特定的名稱完全相同<xref:System.Type>列印系統物件，包括大小寫的屬性。

trans-unit.source: The name of the property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty" /> represents.
The value of the property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty" /> represents.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty" /> class that has the specified property name and value.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty" /> 類別的新執行個體，此類別有指定的屬性名稱與屬性值。

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Type> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: `attributeName`拼字應該做為某些特定的名稱完全相同<xref:System.Type>列印系統物件，包括大小寫的屬性。

trans-unit.source: Provides implicit conversion from a <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty" /> (or from a pointer to such a property) to a <see cref="T:System.Type" /> value.
trans-unit.target: 提供由 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty" /> (或這類屬性的指標) 至 <see cref="T:System.Type" /> 值的隱含轉換。

trans-unit.source: A pointer to the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty" /> that is converted.
Provides implicit conversion to a <see cref="T:System.Type" /> value from a pointer to a <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty" />.
trans-unit.target: 提供由指標的 <see cref="T:System.Type" /> 值至 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty" /> 的隱含轉換。

trans-unit.source: A converted Type value form a PrintSystemTypeProperty object.
trans-unit.target: PrintSystemTypeProperty 物件的轉換後 Type 值。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the value of the property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty" /> represents.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty" /> 表示的屬性值。

trans-unit.source: The value of the property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty" /> represents.
